Title: 109: Business Consultancy in the Space of Data Science
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, we will listen to the CEO and Founder of Business Science LLC, Matt Dancho. You will hear about combining data science with business and finance, learn why data science consultancies are in demand, and learn about the open-source software developed by Business Science.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/109
